Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • Student
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Instate, International, Outstate

    public abstract class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    The Student class defines the properties and methods of a student and implements the Comparable class. Students have a first name, last name and the number of credits they take. Students can compare names and calculate tuition due.
